Package: tubecleanR
Type: Package
Title: Parsing and Preprocessing YouTube Comment and Subtitle Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Julian Kohne; Johannes Breuer
Maintainer: Julian Kohne <julian.kohe@gesis.org>
Description: This mini-package is an extension for the tuber and the vsonSML packages for preprocessing downloaded YouTube comment and subtitle data. The package enables users to clean up comment data by removing and/or replacing links, smileys, emoji, and usernames. The output are well-defined dataframes suitable for further textmining or visualizations.
Imports: anytime, qdapRegex, stringi, utils
License: CC BY-NC 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
